Country, region, and province level COVID-19 time series for Europe

Source: R/eu-data-cache-data.R
eu_data_cache_data.Rd

covid19-eu-data is a dataset repository for COVID-19/SARS-CoV-2 cases in Europe. They pull data from official government websites regularly using the open-source scripts inside the repository.

eu_data_cache_data(datasets = eu_data_cache_datasets(include_ecdc = FALSE))

eu_data_cache_datasets(include_ecdc = TRUE)

Source

  • https://covid19-eu-data-cache.now.sh/

  • https://github.com/covid19-eu-zh/covid19-eu-data

Functions

  • eu_data_cache_datasets:

Note

Some oddities of the dataset are captured on the original site at https://github.com/covid19-eu-zh/covid19-eu-data#notes
